    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Man-made objects such as buoys, lighthouses, lightships, Loran and other electronic systems, which aid mariners in determing position of safe course.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
